Texts.Eng: Bring the ^green;Targeting Chip^reset; to ^orange;me^reset; at the ^orange;Science Outpost^reset;
Good job. The fact that you survived that firepower says much of your prowess in battle. I would not want to mess with you.
On ^green;Cyber Spheres^reset; or ^green;Wastelands^reset; there often walk dangerous battle machines known as ^orange;War Bots^reset;. Take one down, and I'll pay you well.
